<collect_book_scenario_info version="20130401095237">
	<!-- 카드아이템키값, 카드이름, 시나리오  -->
	<scenario_list key="5000011">
		<kor name="클락 래빗 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}앨리스 복장 남자 버전, 여자 복장의 인기에 힘입어 제작된 복장.{N}평소 귀여운 미소년 남자친구를 꿈꾸던 여성 유저 사이에 남자친구 선물용으로 폭발적인 인기를 얻는중{N}주의사항: 똑같은 복장을 입는다고 해서 똑같은 미소년은 될 수 없음"/>
		<ger name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Alice Costume für Jungs. Passt perfekt zum Alice-Look der Mädchen, sodass ihr im Partnerlook gehen könnt. {N}Jeder Alice-Liebhaber sollte dieses Outfit tragen, um seine Freundin zu beeindrucken. {N}Achtung: Dieses Outfit verwandelt euch in einen heißen Feger. Die Ladies werden euch hinterherstarren!"/>
        <eng name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The male Alice Costume. Perfectly fitting with the female Alice look, you can go in partner look. {N} Every Alice lover should wear this costume to impress his girlfriend. {N} Caution: This costume will make you look like a hot hare and ladies will start staring at you.  "/>
		<fre name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Le costume d'Alice pour homme, afin d'être en parfaite harmonie avec sa Alice. {N} Tous les amoureux d'Alice se doivent de porter ce costume pour impressionner leur copine. {N} Mais attention, cette tenue de chaud lapin ne laissera pas tous les cœurs indifférents.  "/>
		<spa name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La vestimenta masculina de Alice. Se ajusta perfectamente a la apariencia femenina de Alice. {N} Los novios de Alice seguramente asombrarán a sus novias con esta vestimenta. {N}Precaución: Con esta vestimenta te verás como un conejito caliente y las chicas no podrán dejar de mirarte!  "/>
		<ita name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il costume di Alice al maschile. Si adatta perfettamente al look femminile di Alice, quindi potrete andare in coppia.{N}Tutti coloro che adorano Alice dovrebbero indossare questo costume per far colpo sulla propria ragazza.{N}Attenzione: questo costume ti farà sembrare un coniglio sensuale e le ragazze inizieranno a fissarti."/>
		<rus name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Мужской вариант Alice Costume идеально подходит под тематику главной героини Alice. {N}Если вам нравится  Alice, то тогда в этом костюме вы произведете отличное впечатление. {N}Предупреждение: Надев этот костюм женские взгляды неизбежны."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Normal Clock Rabbit" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} The male Alice Costume. Dişi Alice görünümüne kusursuzca uyan şekilde partner görünümüne sahip olabilirsin. {N} Her Alice severin, kız arkadaşını etkilemek için bu kostümü giymesi gerekir. {N} Uyarı: Bu kostüm, seni ateşli bir tavşan gibi gösterecek ve tüm bayanlar dik dik sana bakacak. "/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000012">
		<kor name="클락 래빗 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}앨리스 복장 남자 버전, 여자 복장의 인기에 힘입어 제작된 복장.{N}평소 귀여운 미소년 남자친구를 꿈꾸던 여성 유저 사이에 남자친구 선물용으로 폭발적인 인기를 얻는중{N}주의사항: 똑같은 복장을 입는다고 해서 똑같은 미소년은 될 수 없음"/>
		<kor name="클락 래빗 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}앨리스 복장 남자 버전, 여자 복장의 인기에 힘입어 제작된 복장.{N}평소 귀여운 미소년 남자친구를 꿈꾸던 여성 유저 사이에 남자친구 선물용으로 폭발적인 인기를 얻는중{N}주의사항: 똑같은 복장을 입는다고 해서 똑같은 미소년은 될 수 없음"/>
		<ger name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Alice Costume für Jungs. Passt perfekt zum Alice-Look der Mädchen, sodass ihr im Partnerlook gehen könnt. {N}Jeder Alice-Liebhaber sollte dieses Outfit tragen, um seine Freundin zu beeindrucken. {N}Achtung: Dieses Outfit verwandelt euch in einen heißen Feger. Die Ladies werden euch hinterherstarren!"/>
        <eng name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The male Alice Costume. Perfectly fitting with the female Alice look, you can go in partner look. {N} Every Alice lover should wear this costume to impress his girlfriend. {N} Caution: This costume will make you look like a hot hare and ladies will start staring at you.  "/>
		<fre name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Le costume d'Alice pour homme, afin d'être en parfaite harmonie avec sa Alice. {N} Tous les amoureux d'Alice se doivent de porter ce costume pour impressionner leur copine. {N} Mais attention, cette tenue de chaud lapin ne laissera pas tous les cœurs indifférents.  "/>
		<spa name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La vestimenta masculina de Alice. Se ajusta perfectamente a la apariencia femenina de Alice. {N} Los novios de Alice seguramente asombrarán a sus novias con esta vestimenta. {N}Precaución: Con esta vestimenta te verás como un conejito caliente y las chicas no podrán dejar de mirarte!  "/>
		<ita name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il costume di Alice al maschile. Si adatta perfettamente al look femminile di Alice, quindi potrete andare in coppia.{N}Tutti coloro che adorano Alice dovrebbero indossare questo costume per far colpo sulla propria ragazza.{N}Attenzione: questo costume ti farà sembrare un coniglio sensuale e le ragazze inizieranno a fissarti."/>
		<rus name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Мужской вариант Alice Costume идеально подходит под тематику главной героини Alice. {N}Если вам нравится  Alice, то тогда в этом костюме вы произведете отличное впечатление. {N}Предупреждение: Надев этот костюм женские взгляды неизбежны."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Clock Rabbit Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} The male Alice Costume. Dişi Alice görünümüne kusursuzca uyan şekilde partner görünümüne sahip olabilirsin. {N} Her Alice severin, kız arkadaşını etkilemek için bu kostümü giymesi gerekir. {N} Uyarı: Bu kostüm, seni ateşli bir tavşan gibi gösterecek ve tüm bayanlar dik dik sana bakacak. "/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000013">
		<kor name="스마트 앨리스 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}초 다국적 기업 '더 월드'에서 새로운 AI 시스템 개발을 위해 제조한 ALICE에서 영감을 얻어 제작된{N}S4리그 복장으로 유저들 사이에 암암리에 인기 상품으로 등극.{N}한때 복장 제작자가 '인생은 한방이야'를 외치며 고가에 판매를 하였음에도 불구하고 폭발적인 인기를 얻음."/>
		<ger name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Das neue von Alice inspirierte Outfit. Dies ist AI-System der nächsten Generation, das von der Firma 'The World' entwickelt wurde.{N}Dieses Outfit wurde heimlich an S4 League-Spieler verkauft.{N}Die Designer dieses Kostüms sind der Meinung, dass es nur von den besten Spielern getragen werden sollte"/>
        <eng name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The new costume that is inspired by Alice. This is the Next Gen AI system {N}created by the company called 'The World',{N}This costume was secretly sold to S4 League users.{N}The designers of this costume believe that this costume should only be worn by the best players."/>
		<fre name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Le tout nouveau costume inspiré de l'univers d'Alice. Il s'agit du système d'I.A. Next-Gen crée par une mystérieuse compagnie répondant au nom de 'The World'{N} Ce costume fut vendu illégalement aux joueurs d'S4 League.{N}Ses créateurs avaient pour habitude de dire qu'il était n'était réservé qu'aux meilleurs joueurs."/>
		<spa name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La nueva vestimenta inspirada por Alice. Este es el sistema AI de la próxima generación realizado por la compañía llamada 'The World'.{N}Esta vestimenta fue vendida en forma secreta a los usuarios de S4 League.{N}Los diseñadores de este traje creen que esta vestimenta debería ser usada sólo por los mejores jugadores."/>
		<ita name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il nuovo costume ispirato a Alice. Questo è il sistema AI di ultima generazione sviluppato dalla società 'The World'.{N}Questo costume è stato venduto in segreto agli utenti di S4 League.{N}I suoi designer ritengono che debba essere indossato solo dai giocatori migliori."/>
		<rus name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Новый костюм в стиле Alice. Его разработали по системе Next Gen AI компанией The World,{N} который позже был тайно распродан S4 League игрокам.{N}Дизайнеры этого костюма считают, что этот костюм достояны носить только лучшие игроки."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Normal Smart Alice" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Alice'den esinlenilen yeni kostüm. Bu, 'The World' adlı şirketin yarattığı Gelecek Nesil Yapay Zeka sistemi,{N}Bu kostüm, gizlice S4 League kullanıcılarına satıldı.{N}Bu kostümün tasarımcıları, kostümün sadece en iyi oyuncular tarafından giyilmesi gerektiğine inanıyor."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000014">
		<kor name="스마트 앨리스 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}초 다국적 기업 '더 월드'에서 새로운 AI 시스템 개발을 위해 제조한 ALICE에서 영감을 얻어 제작된{N}S4리그 복장으로 유저들 사이에 암암리에 인기 상품으로 등극.{N}한때 복장 제작자가 '인생은 한방이야'를 외치며 고가에 판매를 하였음에도 불구하고 폭발적인 인기를 얻음."/>
		<ger name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Das neue von Alice inspirierte Outfit. Dies ist AI-System der nächsten Generation, das von der Firma 'The World' entwickelt wurde.{N}Dieses Outfit wurde heimlich an S4 League-Spieler verkauft.{N}Die Designer dieses Kostüms sind der Meinung, dass es nur von den besten Spielern getragen werden sollte"/>
        <eng name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The new costume that is inspired by Alice. This is the Next Gen AI system {N}created by the company called 'The World',{N}This costume was secretly sold to S4 League users.{N}The designers of this costume believe that this costume should only be worn by the best players."/>
		<fre name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Le tout nouveau costume inspiré de l'univers d'Alice. Il s'agit du système d'I.A. Next-Gen crée par une mystérieuse compagnie répondant au nom de 'The World'{N} Ce costume fut vendu illégalement aux joueurs d'S4 League.{N}Ses créateurs avaient pour habitude de dire qu'il était n'était réservé qu'aux meilleurs joueurs."/>
		<spa name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La nueva vestimenta inspirada por Alice. Este es el sistema AI de la próxima generación realizado por la compañía llamada 'The World'.{N}Esta vestimenta fue vendida en forma secreta a los usuarios de S4 League.{N}Los diseñadores de este traje creen que esta vestimenta debería ser usada sólo por los mejores jugadores."/>
		<ita name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il nuovo costume ispirato a Alice. Questo è il sistema AI di ultima generazione sviluppato dalla società 'The World'.{N}Questo costume è stato venduto in segreto agli utenti di S4 League.{N}I suoi designer ritengono che debba essere indossato solo dai giocatori migliori."/>
		<rus name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Новый костюм в стиле Alice. Его разработали по системе Next Gen AI компанией The World,{N} который позже был тайно распродан S4 League игрокам.{N}Дизайнеры этого костюма считают, что этот костюм достояны носить только лучшие игроки."/>>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Smart Alice Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Alice'den esinlenilen yeni kostüm. Bu, 'The World' adlı şirketin yarattığı Gelecek Nesil Yapay Zeka sistemi,{N}Bu kostüm, gizlice S4 League kullanıcılarına satıldı.{N}Bu kostümün tasarımcıları, kostümün sadece en iyi oyuncular tarafından giyilmesi gerektiğine inanıyor."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000015">
		<kor name="다크 어쌔신 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}한때 암살자를 동경했던 제작자가 은밀하고 어둡게를 컨셉으로 제작한 복장{N}컨퀘스트 모드에서 AI를 상대로 싸울때 입으면 적절한 복장. 활동성에 용이함.{N}단, 도둑으로 오해받을 수 있으니 조심하시길."/>
		<ger name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es ist immer gefährlich, in die Höhle des Drachen zu gehen. Um eine Chance gegen die virtuellen Drachen zu haben, musst du dieses Kostüm tragen! Es besteht aus einem speziellen Stoff, der schnelle und lautlose Bewegungen im Dunklen erlaubt. {N}Dieses Outfit ist PERFEKT für den Eroberungsmodus, wenn man gegen die AI kämpft. Es ist elastisch und leicht."/>
        <eng name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It is always dangerous to venture into a dragon's den, you need to wear {N}this costume to have a chance against the virtual dragons! {N}The costume is made out of a a special fabric and allows the user to move fast and silently in the darkness. {N}This costume is THE perfect costume for the conquest mode when battling the AI. {N}It is flexible and light. "/>
		<fre name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il est toujours périlleux de pénétrer dans l'antre d'un dragon, et si vous voulez avoir une chance contre les dragons virtuels, vous feriez mieux de revêtir ce costume ! Fabriqué dans l'étoffe la plus rare, il permet de se faufiler rapidement dans l'obscurité. {N}C'est LE costume parfait en mode Conquest pour affronter les I.A : il est souple et léger."/>
		<spa name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Siempre es peligroso aventurarse dentro de la guarida de un dragón, así que tienes que usar este traje para tener una chance contra los dragones virtuales! El traje está realizado con una tela especial y le permite al usuario moverse rápida y silenciosamente en la oscuridad. {N}Este traje es PERFECTO para el modo Conquest cuando luchas contra el AI. Es flexible y ligero. "/>
		<ita name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}E' sempre pericoloso addentrarsi nella tana di un drago, quindi è necessario indossare questo costume per avere una possibilità contro i draghi virtuali! Il costume è fatto di un tessuto speciale e permette di muoversi rapidamente e silenziosamente nell'oscurità.{N}E' IL costume perfetto in Conquest Mode contro l'AI. E' elasticizzato e leggero. "/>
		<rus name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Заглядывая в драконье логово, вы всегда рискуете жизнью, поэтому вам необходим специальный костюм, чтобы противостоять виртуальным драконам! Этот костюм разработан из специального материала, который позволит вам быстро и тихо передвигаться в темноте. {N}Это лучший вариант в борьбе против AI в режиме Conquest – легкий и удобный костюм."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Dark Assassin Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bir ejderhanın inine girmek hep tehlikeli olmuştur, bu nedenle sanal ejderhalara karşı bir şansın olması için bu kostümü giymelisin! Bu kostüm, özel bir kumaştan yapılmıştır ve kullanıcının karanlıkta hızla ve sessizce hareket etmesini sağlar. {N}Bu kostüm, yapay zekayla savaşırken zafer modu için EN iyi kostümdür. Esnek ve hafiftir. "/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000016">
		<kor name="다크 어쌔신 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}한때 암살자를 동경했던 제작자가 은밀하고 어둡게를 컨셉으로 제작한 복장{N}컨퀘스트 모드에서 AI를 상대로 싸울때 입으면 적절한 복장. 활동성에 용이함.{N}단, 도둑으로 오해받을 수 있으니 조심하시길"/>
		<ger name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es ist immer gefährlich, in die Höhle des Drachen zu gehen. Um eine Chance gegen die virtuellen Drachen zu haben, musst du dieses Kostüm tragen! Es besteht aus einem speziellen Stoff, der schnelle und lautlose Bewegungen im Dunklen erlaubt. {N}Dieses Outfit ist PERFEKT für den Eroberungsmodus, wenn man gegen die AI kämpft. Es ist elastisch und leicht."/>
        <eng name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It is always dangerous to venture into a dragon's den, you need to wear {N}this costume to have a chance against the virtual dragons! {N}The costume is made out of a a special fabric and allows the user to move fast and silently in the darkness. {N}This costume is THE perfect costume for the conquest mode when battling the AI. {N}It is flexible and light. "/>
		<fre name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il est toujours périlleux de pénétrer dans l'antre d'un dragon, et si vous voulez avoir une chance contre les dragons virtuels, vous feriez mieux de revêtir ce costume ! Fabriqué dans l'étoffe la plus rare, il permet de se faufiler rapidement dans l'obscurité. {N}C'est LE costume parfait en mode Conquest pour affronter les I.A : il est souple et léger."/>
		<spa name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Siempre es peligroso aventurarse dentro de la guarida de un dragón, así que tienes que usar este traje para tener una chance contra los dragones virtuales! El traje está realizado con una tela especial y le permite al usuario moverse rápida y silenciosamente en la oscuridad. {N}Este traje es PERFECTO para el modo Conquest cuando luchas contra el AI. Es flexible y ligero. "/>
		<ita name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}E' sempre pericoloso addentrarsi nella tana di un drago, quindi è necessario indossare questo costume per avere una possibilità contro i draghi virtuali! Il costume è fatto di un tessuto speciale e permette di muoversi rapidamente e silenziosamente nell'oscurità.{N}E' IL costume perfetto in Conquest Mode contro l'AI. E' elasticizzato e leggero. "/>
		<rus name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Заглядывая в драконье логово, вы всегда рискуете жизнью, поэтому вам необходим специальный костюм, чтобы противостоять виртуальным драконам! Этот костюм разработан из специального материала, который позволит вам быстро и тихо передвигаться в темноте. {N}Это лучший вариант в борьбе против AI в режиме Conquest – легкий и удобный костюм."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Dark Assassin Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bir ejderhanın inine girmek hep tehlikeli olmuştur, bu nedenle sanal ejderhalara karşı bir şansın olması için bu kostümü giymelisin! Bu kostüm, özel bir kumaştan yapılmıştır ve kullanıcının karanlıkta hızla ve sessizce hareket etmesini sağlar. {N}Bu kostüm, yapay zekayla savaşırken zafer modu için EN iyi kostümdür. Esnek ve hafiftir. "/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000017">
		<kor name="위키드 조커 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}암살자의 여자 버전 복장. 애초 다크 어쌔신 복장과 동일한 컨셉으로 제작 되었으나,{N}제작자의 사심이 들어가 섹시한 복장으로 재 탄생{N}평소 멋있는 여자 암살자를 동경했던 유저라면 한번쯤 입어보길 권장하고 싶은 복장"/>
		<ger name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Die Version des Dark Assassin für Mädchen hat weniger Stoff. {N}Deswegen ist es nicht nur leichter, sondern auch um Einiges sexier. {N}Sei aber gewarnt - dieses Kostüm macht dich schnell wie der Blitz!"/>
        <eng name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The female version of the Dark Assassin has less fabric. {N} Therefore, it is not only lighter, but way sexier. {N} Be aware though, this costume also makes you as fast as lightning!"/>
		<fre name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La version femme du Sombre Assassin est composée de moins d'étoffe. {N} De ce fait, il n'est pas seulement plus léger, il est aussi diablement plus torride. {N} Ne vous y méprenez pas ce costume vous rendra également aussi rapide que la foudre !"/>
		<spa name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La versión femenina del Dark Assassin poseee menos tela. {N} Por lo tanto, es más ligero y más atractivo. {N} Pero hay que tener en cuenta que con esta vestimenta también serás tan veloz como un rayo!"/>
		<ita name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La versione femminile del Dark Assassin ha meno tessuto.{N}Per questo motivo, non è solo più leggera, ma anche molto più seducente.{N}Fai attenzione, questo costume ti rende veloce come un lampo!"/>
		<rus name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Модель костюма Dark Assassin для девушек. Для его разработки использовалось меньше ткани,{N}поэтому он не только легче, но и сексуальней! {N}Но будьте осторожны, в этом костюме вы преодолеете скорость света!"/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Wicked Joker Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dark Assassin'in dişi versiyonunda daha az kumaş kullanılmıştır. {N} Bu nedenle hem daha hafif hem de çok daha çekicidir. {N} Ama dikkatli ol, bu kostüm seni şimşek gibi hızlı yapacak!"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000018">
		<kor name="위키드 조커 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}암살자의 여자 버전 복장. 애초 다크 어쌔신 복장과 동일한 컨셉으로 제작 되었으나,{N}제작자의 사심이 들어가 섹시한 복장으로 재 탄생{N}평소 멋있는 여자 암살자를 동경했던 유저라면 한번쯤 입어보길 권장하고 싶은 복장"/>
		<ger name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Die Version des Dark Assassin für Mädchen hat weniger Stoff. {N}Deswegen ist es nicht nur leichter, sondern auch um Einiges sexier. {N}Sei aber gewarnt - dieses Kostüm macht dich schnell wie der Blitz!"/>
        <eng name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The female version of the Dark Assassin has less fabric. {N} Therefore, it is not only lighter, but way sexier. {N} Be aware though, this costume also makes you as fast as lightning!"/>
		<fre name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La version femme du Sombre Assassin est composée de moins d'étoffe. {N} De ce fait, il n'est pas seulement plus léger, il est aussi diablement plus torride. {N} Ne vous y méprenez pas ce costume vous rendra également aussi rapide que la foudre !"/>
		<spa name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La versión femenina del Dark Assassin poseee menos tela. {N} Por lo tanto, es más ligero y más atractivo. {N} Pero hay que tener en cuenta que con esta vestimenta también serás tan veloz como un rayo!"/>
		<ita name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La versione femminile del Dark Assassin ha meno tessuto.{N}Per questo motivo, non è solo più leggera, ma anche molto più seducente.{N}Fai attenzione, questo costume ti rende veloce come un lampo!"/>
		<rus name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Модель костюма Dark Assassin для девушек. Для его разработки использовалось меньше ткани,{N}поэтому он не только легче, но и сексуальней! {N}Но будьте осторожны, в этом костюме вы преодолеете скорость света!"/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Wicked Joker Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dark Assassin'in dişi versiyonunda daha az kumaş kullanılmıştır. {N} Bu nedenle hem daha hafif hem de çok daha çekicidir. {N} Ama dikkatli ol, bu kostüm seni şimşek gibi hızlı yapacak!"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000019">
		<kor name="스페셜 웨이터  일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}시크한 듯 무심해 보이는 웨이터에 영감을 얻어 제작된 복장.{N}웨이터의 목장갑은 이 복장에 하이라이트라고 할 수 있음."/>
		<ger name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm wurde von der Kellneruniform eines vornehmen Restaurants inspiriert.{N}Man sagt, es werde von Agenten und Ninjas zur Tarnung benutzt."/>
        <eng name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A costume that has been inspired by a waiters uniform from a posh restaurant. {N}Some say it has been used as a disguise by agents and ninjas. "/>
		<fre name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume inspiré de la tenue des serveurs des plus grands restaurants. {N}Certains disent qu'il a servi de couverture pour des agents secrets et des ninjas."/>
		<spa name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Una vestimenta inspirada en un uniforme de camarero de un restaurant lujoso. {N}Algunos dicen que ha sido utilizada como disfraz por agentes y ninjas."/>
		<ita name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume ispirato all'uniforme dei camerieri di un ristorante elegante.{N}Alcuni dicono che sia stato usato come travestimento da agenti e ninja."/>
		<rus name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Улучшенный костюм официанта из шикарного ресторана. {N}Ходят слухи, что его используют для маскировки агентов и ниндзя."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Special Waiter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Şık bir restoranda çalışan bir garsondan ilham alınarak hazırlanan bir kostüm. {N}Bunun ajanlar ve ninjalar tarafından kimliklerini gizlemek için kullanıldığına dair söylentiler mevcuttur."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000020">
		<kor name="스페셜 웨이터  유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}시크한 듯 무심해 보이는 웨이터에 영감을 얻어 제작된 복장.{N}웨이터의 목장갑은 이 복장에 하이라이트라고 할 수 있음."/>
		<ger name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm wurde von der Kellneruniform eines vornehmen Restaurants inspiriert.{N}Man sagt, es werde von Agenten und Ninjas zur Tarnung benutzt."/>
        <eng name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A costume that has been inspired by a waiters uniform from a posh restaurant. {N}Some say it has been used as a disguise by agents and ninjas. "/>
		<fre name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume inspiré de la tenue des serveurs des plus grands restaurants. {N}Certains disent qu'il a servi de couverture pour des agents secrets et des ninjas."/>
		<spa name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Una vestimenta inspirada en un uniforme de camarero de un restaurant lujoso. {N}Algunos dicen que ha sido utilizada como disfraz por agentes y ninjas."/>
		<ita name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume ispirato all'uniforme dei camerieri di un ristorante elegante.{N}Alcuni dicono che sia stato usato come travestimento da agenti e ninja."/>
		<rus name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Улучшенный костюм официанта из шикарного ресторана. {N}Ходят слухи, что его используют для маскировки агентов и ниндзя."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Special Waiter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Şık bir restoranda çalışan bir garsondan ilham alınarak hazırlanan bir kostüm. {N}Bunun ajanlar ve ninjalar tarafından kimliklerini gizlemek için kullanıldığına dair söylentiler mevcuttur."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000021">
		<kor name="러블리 쿡  일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}아무리 맛없는 요리를 만드는 요리사라도 이 복장을 입고 만들면 베스트 요리사로 추천 될 것만 같은 복장{N}세트로 출시된 거대한 프라이팬 (스톰 배트 유니크)은 요리사 복장과 함께 꼭 구매해야 할 핫 아이템~!"/>
		<ger name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm könnte dich zum besten Koch der Welt machen.{N} Nein, im Ernst! Allerdings wird es auch von Spionen zusammen mit der Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) als Waffe benutzt!"/>
        <eng name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A costume that might be able to turn you into the world's greatest chef. {N} No, not for real. But this costume was also used by agents, along with the Frying Pan {N}(Storm Bat Unique) as a weapon!"/>
		<fre name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume qui pourrait bien vous transformer en cordon bleu ! {N} Enfin non, pas vraiment. Mais tout de même, ce costume a été utilisé par des agents secrets avec la Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) en guise d'arme !"/>
		<spa name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un traje que podría convertirte en el mejor chef del mundo. {N} No, no es verdad. Pero este traje también ha sido utilizado por agentes, junto con el Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) como arma."/>
		<ita name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume che potrebbe farti diventare lo chef più importante del mondo.{N}No, non davvero. Questo costume è stato usato anche da alcuni agenti con la Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) come arma!"/>
		<rus name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Костюм, в котором вы станете поваром мирового уровня. {N} Но это не правда! Его используют для маскировки агентов, которые вооружены Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) в качестве оружия!"/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Lovely Cook Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dünyanın en iyi şefine dönüşmeni sağlayabilecek bir kostüm. {N}Şaka, şaka. Ama bu kostüm de silah olarak bir tava (Storm Bat Unique) ile ajanlar tarafından kullanılmıştır!"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000022">
		<kor name="러블리 쿡  유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}아무리 맛없는 요리를 만드는 요리사라도 이 복장을 입고 만들면 베스트 요리사로 추천 될 것만 같은 복장{N}세트로 출시된 거대한 프라이팬 (스톰 배트 유니크)은 요리사 복장과 함께 꼭 구매해야 할 핫 아이템~!"/>
		<ger name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm könnte dich zum besten Koch der Welt machen.{N} Nein, im Ernst! Allerdings wird es auch von Spionen zusammen mit der Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) als Waffe benutzt!"/>
         <eng name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A costume that might be able to turn you into the world's greatest chef. {N} No, not for real. But this costume was also used by agents, along with the Frying Pan {N}(Storm Bat Unique) as a weapon!"/>
		<fre name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume qui pourrait bien vous transformer en cordon bleu ! {N} Enfin non, pas vraiment. Mais tout de même, ce costume a été utilisé par des agents secrets avec la Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) en guise d'arme !"/>
		<spa name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un traje que podría convertirte en el mejor chef del mundo. {N} No, no es verdad. Pero este traje también ha sido utilizado por agentes, junto con el Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) como arma."/>
		<ita name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un costume che potrebbe farti diventare lo chef più importante del mondo.{N}No, non davvero. Questo costume è stato usato anche da alcuni agenti con la Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) come arma!"/>
		<rus name="Lovely Cook Unique "data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Костюм, в котором вы станете поваром мирового уровня. {N} Но это не правда! Его используют для маскировки агентов, которые вооружены Frying Pan (Storm Bat Unique) в качестве оружия!"/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Lovely Cook Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dünyanın en iyi şefine dönüşmeni sağlayabilecek bir kostüm. {N}Şaka, şaka. Ama bu kostüm de silah olarak bir tava (Storm Bat Unique) ile ajanlar tarafından kullanılmıştır!"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000023">
		<kor name="쿵푸 파이터 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}소림사 제자들을 위해 특별히 제작된 복장으로 싸움을 못하는 유저라도{N}쿵푸 파이터 복장만 입으면 최고의 파이터가 될 수 있다는 전설이 있는 복장 아이템"/>
		<ger name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm wurde speziell für Schüler der Shaolin entworfen.{N}Wie es scheint, verbessert es Kampftechniken und macht dich zum besten Kämpfer der ganzen Welt."/>
        <eng name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}This costume is specially designed for the disciples of Shaolin. {N} This costume looks like it can boost fighting techniques and turn you into the worlds best fighter."/>
		<fre name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ce costume a été spécialement conçu pour les disciples des Shaolins. {N} Ce costume donne le sentiment d'être invincible et vous fera devenir l'un des meilleurs guerriers du monde. "/>
		<spa name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Este traje está especialmente diseñado para los discípulos de Shaolin. {N} Con esta vestimenta podrás mejorar tus técnicas de lucha y te convertirá en el mejor luchador del mundo."/>
		<ita name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Questo costume è stato ideato per gli allievi di Shaolin.{N}Sembra possa potenziare le tecniche di combattimento e farti diventare il miglior lottatore del mondo."/>
		<rus name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Специальный костюм для Шаолинь учеников. {N}Этот костюм придаст вам боевой дух и направит на путь лучшего в мире бойца."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Kung Fu fighter Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bu kostüm, özellikle Shaolin havarileri için tasarlanmıştır. {N} Bu kostüm, dövüş tekniklerini destekleyebilecek ve seni dünyanın en iyi dövüşçüsüne dönüştürebilecekmiş gibi görünüyor."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000024">
		<kor name="쿵푸 파이터 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}소림사 제자들을 위해 특별히 제작된 복장으로 싸움을 못하는 유저라도{N}쿵푸 파이터 복장만 입으면 최고의 파이터가 될 수 있다는 전설이 있는 복장 아이템"/>
		<ger name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm wurde speziell für Schüler der Shaolin entworfen.{N}Wie es scheint, verbessert es Kampftechniken und macht dich zum besten Kämpfer der ganzen Welt."/>
                <eng name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}This costume is specially designed for the disciples of Shaolin. {N} This costume looks like it can boost fighting techniques and turn you into the worlds best fighter."/>
		<fre name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ce costume a été spécialement conçu pour les disciples des Shaolins. {N} Ce costume donne le sentiment d'être invincible et vous fera devenir l'un des meilleurs guerriers du monde. "/>
		<spa name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Este traje está especialmente diseñado para los discípulos de Shaolin. {N} Con esta vestimenta podrás mejorar tus técnicas de lucha y te convertirá en el mejor luchador del mundo."/>
		<ita name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Questo costume è stato ideato per gli allievi di Shaolin.{N}Sembra possa potenziare le tecniche di combattimento e farti diventare il miglior lottatore del mondo."/>
		<rus name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Специальный костюм для Шаолинь учеников. {N}Этот костюм придаст вам боевой дух и направит на путь лучшего в мире бойца."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Kung Fu fighter Unique"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bu kostüm, özellikle Shaolin havarileri için tasarlanmıştır. {N} Bu kostüm, dövüş tekniklerini destekleyebilecek ve seni dünyanın en iyi dövüşçüsüne dönüştürebilecekmiş gibi görünüyor."/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000025">
		<kor name="치파오 걸 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} 치파오 걸 복장을 입는 순간 앙증맞은 만두머리가 귀여움을 한껏 돋보이게 하며,{N}남자들의 가슴을 콩닥콩닥 뛰게 함.{N}하나쯤은 소장하고 싶은 욕구를 불러일으키는 복장 아이템"/>
		<ger name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es heißt, dieses Kostüm habe einst einer sehr berühmten Kämpferin aus China gehört.{N}Jeder, der es trägt, sollte es zu Ehren dieser Kämpferin tragen!"/>
        <eng name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} It is said that this costume once belonged to a very famous fighting girl from China. {N} Everyone wearing it shall honor this female fighter!"/>
		<fre name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}On raconte que ce costume appartenait jadis à une célèbre guerrière de Chine. {N} Porter cette tenue est perçu comme un hommage à cette guerrière ! "/>
		<spa name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} Se dice que este traje perteneció alguna vez a una famosa luchadora en China. {N} El que lo use, honrará a esta luchadora!"/>
		<ita name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Pare che questo costume sia appartenuto a una famosa lottatrice cinese.{N}Chi lo indosserà dovrà onorarla"/>
		<rus name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Этот костюм принадлежал самой сильной девушке в Китае. {N}Каждый, кто носит этот костюм, должен уважать бойцовский дух его первого обладателя!"/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<tur name="Chipao Girl Normal"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} Bu kostümün bir zamanlar çok ünlü Çinli bir kıza ait olduğu söylenir. {N} Bunu giyen herkes, bu dişi dövüşçüyü onurlandırmalıdır!"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000026">
		<kor name="치파오 걸 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} 치파오 걸 복장을 입는 순간 앙증맞은 만두머리가 귀여움을 한껏 돋보이게 하며,{N}남자들의 가슴을 콩닥콩닥 뛰게 함.{N}하나쯤은 소장하고 싶은 욕구를 불러일으키는 복장 아이템"/>
