	<scenario_list key="5000027">
		<kor name="2013 어드벤쳐 펌비 컬렉션" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}기대하시라..두둥..2013 시즌 어드벤쳐가 곧 오픈 됩니다.{N}시즌 오픈을 기념하여 펌비들이 시즌 옷을 입고 여러분들을 맞이하고 있어요!{N}귀여운 펌비 컬렉션 한번 모아보실래요?{N}푸짐한 보상이 여러분을 기다리고 있답니다! 와우! 컬렉팅 북 기본 보상과 시즌 아이템을 획득할 수 있어요!"/>
		<ger name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bleibt dran, denn die zweite Season für 2013 beginnt bald!{N}Um den Start der neuen Season zu feiern, wird unser Fumbi vorab die neuen Kostüme vorstellen.{N}Sammelt unsere Fumbis und gehört zu den ersten, die unsere nächsten Kostüme sehen dürfen.{N}Euch erwarten großartige Belohnungen!"/>
        <eng name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Stay tuned, the new season for the 2013 is about to be launched. {N}To celebrate the launch of the new season, {N}Our fumbi will introduce upcoming new costume in advance. {N}Collect our fumbi and be the first one to preview our upcoming costume. {N}Also, there will be an aswesome reward waiting for you!!"/>
		<fre name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Attention, le deuxième saison de l'année 2013 est sur le point de commencer! {N} À cette occasion, notre Fumbi vous présentera les nouveaux costumes en exclusivité. {N}Récupérez nos Fumbis et soyez le premier à avoir un aperçu de nos nouveaux costumes.{N}Des récompenses vous attendent !"/>
		<spa name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}¡Manténte atento! La segunda temporada de 2013 está por comenzar!{N} Para celebrar el lanzamiento de la nueva temporada, nuestro Fumbi nos adelantará los nuevos Costumes. {N}Recoge nuestros Fumbis y podrás ser el primero en ver nuestros próximos Costumes. {N}¡Te esperan premios espectaculares!"/>
		<ita name="Collezione Fumbi cacciatore di tesori 2013" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Torna a trovarci! La seconda stagione per il 2013 sta per essere lanciata! {N} Per festeggiare il lancio di questa nuova stagione, il nostro Fumbi presenterà in anteprima i nuovi costumi. {N}Raccogli i nostri Fumbi e metti per primo gli occhi sui costumi in arrivo. {N}Ricche ricompense ti attendono!"/>
		<rus name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Оставайтесь с нами! Приближается второй сезон 2013-го года! {N}Чтобы отпраздновать запуск нового сезона наш Fumbi подготовил особые сезонные костюмы. {N}Соберите всех Fumbi и станьте первым, кто опробует нашу новую коллекцию. {N}Вас ожидают отличные награды!"/>
		<tha name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Stay tuned, the new season for the 2013 is about to be launched. {N} To celebrate the launch of new season, our fumbi will introduce upcoming new costume in advance. {N}Collect our fumbi and be the first one to preview our upcoming costume. {N}Also, there will be aswesome reward is waiting for you!!"/>
		<twn name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Stay tuned, the new season for the 2013 is about to be launched. {N} To celebrate the launch of new season, our fumbi will introduce upcoming new costume in advance. {N}Collect our fumbi and be the first one to preview our upcoming costume. {N}Also, there will be aswesome reward is waiting for you!!"/>
		<tur name="2013 Hazine avcısı fumbi koleksiyonu" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bizimle kal, 2013 için ikinci sezon başlamak üzere! {N} Yeni sezonun başlangıcını kutlamak için, Fumbi'miz gelen yeni kostümleri önceden dahil ediyor. {N}Fumbi'lerimizi topla ve yeni gelecek kostümleri inceleyen ilk kişi ol. {N}İnanılmaz ödüller seni bekliyor olacak!"/>
		<idn name="2013 Treasure hunter fumbi collection" scn="detective_pumby" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Stay tuned, the new season for the 2013 is about to be launched. {N} To celebrate the launch of new season, our fumbi will introduce upcoming new costume in advance. {N}Collect our fumbi and be the first one to preview our upcoming costume. {N}Also, there will be aswesome reward is waiting for you!!"/>
		</scenario_list>
		<scenario_list key="5000028">
		<kor name="워터 스포츠 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}여름에는 시원한 복장을 입어야 제 맛이죠!{N}한시라도 빨리 바캉스를 떠나고 싶게 만드는 복장 아이템!"/>
		<ger name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Erlebt einen besonders coolen Sommer mit dem Water Sports Costume.{N}Ihr werdet euch fühlen, als wärt ihr mitten im Meer!"/>
        <eng name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Experience the cool summer by using the Water Sports costume! {N}It will make you feel like you are in the ocean."/>
		<fre name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Profitez de l'été bien au frais grâce au costume Water Sport.  {N} Avec à cette tenue, vous aurez l'impression d'être littéralement dans l'eau."/>
		<spa name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Experimenta un verano espectacular usando el Water Sport Costume. {N} Te hará sentir como que estás dentro del océano. "/>
		<ita name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Rinfrescati in estate usando il Water Sport Costume. {N} Ti sentirai come se stessi nell'oceano. "/>
		<rus name="Normal Water Sports" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Горячий опыт в жаркий день лета вместе с Water Sport Costume. {N}В этом костюме вы почувствуете себя как в прохладных водах океана."/>
		<tur name="Normal Su Sporları" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Su Sporları Kostümünü kullanarak özellikle harika bir yaz yaşa. {N} Bu, doğrudan sanki okyanustaymışsın gibi hissettirecek. "/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
