		<scenario_list key="5000030">
		<kor name="볼륨 비키니 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}무더운 여름에는 바다로 떠나요!{N}노출도와 방어력이 반비례하는 걸 느낄 수 있는 신기한 복장 아이템!"/>
		<ger name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es ist Zeit, an den Strand zu gehen!{N}Dieses Kostüm wird beweisen, wie sexy ihr seid!"/>
        <eng name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It's time to go to the beach!{N}This costume will show how sexy you are! "/>
		<fre name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il est temps d'aller à la plage !{N}Ce costume révèlera votre naturel sexy !"/>
		<spa name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}¡Es tiempo de ir a la playa!{N}Con este Costume te verás muy sexy! "/>
		<ita name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}È tempo di andare in spiaggia!{N}Questo costume ti dimostrerà quanto sei sexy! "/>
		<rus name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Пора идти на пляж!{N}В этом костюме вы выглядите неотразимо!"/>
		<tha name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It's time for the ocean.!{N}This costume will express your sexyness to others!"/>
		<twn name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It's time for the ocean.!{N}This costume will express your sexyness to others!"/>
		<tur name="Normal Seksi Yaz Bikinisi" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Plaja gitme zamanı geldi!{N}Bu kostüm ne kadar seksi olduğunu gösterecek! "/>
		<idn name="Normal Sexy Summer Bikini" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}It's time for the ocean.!{N}This costume will express your sexyness to others!"/>
