	<scenario_list key="5000056">
      	<kor name="버닝 윈터 보이 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨울을 버티기 위한{N}남자 리거의 필수 복장! 아무리 추워도 따뜻한 패딩과 털모자가 있으면 끄떡 없답니다!!"/>
		<ger name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Mach es dir im Winter mit diesem brennenden Winteroutfit warm und gemütlich.{N}Achtung: Dieses Kostüm hat nichts mit dem Burning Mode zu tun."/>
        <eng name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Keep yourself warm and comfortable during the winter by wearing the Burning Winter Costume.{N}Alert: This costume has nothing to do with burning mode."/>
		<fre name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Restez bien confortablement au chaud tout l'hiver avec le costume Burning Winter.{N}Attention : ce costume n'a rien à voir avec le mode Embrasement."/>
		<spa name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Podrás mantenerte cálido y cómodo durante el invierno con el Burning Winter Costume.{N}Aviso: Este conjunto no tiene nada que ver con la modalidad Burning."/>
		<ita name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il Burning Winter Costume ti offrirà calore e comodità durante l'inverno.{N}Attenzione: questo costume non c'entra nulla con il burning mode."/>
		<rus name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Надев Burning Winter костюм, вам будет тепло и удобство даже в самую холодную зиму. Внимание: Этот костюм не связан с Burning системой."/>
		<tur name="Burning Winter Boy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Burning Winter Costume giyerek kış boyunca kendinizi sıcak ve konforlu tutun. Uyarı: Bu kostümün burning mod ile bir ilgisi yoktur."/>
