<scenario_list key="5000064">
	    
      	<kor name="남자무도복" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨울을 버티기 위한{N}남자 리거의 필수 복장! 아무리 추워도 따뜻한 패딩과 털모자가 있으면 끄떡 없답니다!!"/>
		<ger name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Möge der Kampf beginnen!{N}Ist der Martial Arts Master stark genug?{N}Sieh selbst, was er kann!"/>
        <eng name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The fight may begin!{N}Is Martial Arts Master strong enough? {N}See what he can do."/>
		<fre name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Que le combat commence !{N}Le Maître d'Arts Martiaux est-il assez puissant ? {N}Voyons ce dont il est capable."/>
		<spa name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)"data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}¡La lucha puede comenzar!{N}¿Es Martial Arts Master lo suficientemente poderoso? {N}Fíjate lo que es capaz de hacer."/>
		<ita name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Il combattimento può cominciare!{N}Il Martial Arts Master è abbastanza potente? {N}Guarda quello che riesce a fare."/>
		<rus name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Да начнется битва!{N}Будет ли Martial Arts Master достаточно силен? Узнайте, на что он способен."/>
		<tur name="Martial Arts Master(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Savaş başlayabilir!{N}Martial Arts Master yeterince güçlü mü? {N}Neler yapabileceğini gör."/>
