    <scenario_list key="5000068">
		
        <kor name="프로즌리더" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Maßgefertigter Anzug für Männer von The World,{N}der auf 'Lilith MK2' basiert.{N}Probiere ihn in Season 7 aus!"/>
        <eng name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Specially customized male suit from The World{N}Upgraded base 'Lilith MK2'!!{N}Try it on Season 7!"/>
		<fre name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ce costume pour garçons a été spécialement conçu par The World.{N}'Lilith MK2' en version améliorée !{N}Essayez-le dans la Saison 7 !"/>
		<spa name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Conjunto masculino especialmente personalizado de The World{N}¡¡Una nueva 'Lilith MK2'!!{N}¡Pruébala en la Season 7!"/>
		<ita name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume maschile appositamente personalizzato da The World{N}Migliorato in base a 'Lilith MK2'!!{N}Provalo nella stagione 7!"/>
		<rus name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11{CB-255,255,255,255}Специализированный мужской костюм от корпорации The World. {N}Улучшенный костюм с кодовым названием Lilith MK2!! {N}Примерьте его в Season 7!"/>
		<tur name="Forst Leader(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The World'den özelleştirilmiş erkek kostümü{N}'Lilith MK2'ye uygun olarak yükseltildi!!{N}Sezon 7'de mutlaka deneyin!"/>
