    <scenario_list key="5000070">
		
        <kor name="프로즌릴리트" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith wurde mit neuem Look wiedergeboren! Der neue Name: 'Lilith MK2'.{N}'Lilith MK2' hat jetzt die Unterstützung von The World.{N}Wer kann sie noch aufhalten?"/>
        <eng name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith is revived with new look! New name, 'Lilith MK2'{N}More powerful 'Lilith MK2' with the support of The World.{N}Who can stop her?"/>
		<fre name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith fait son grand retour, plus belle que jamais ! Un nouveau nom 'Lilith MK2'{N}Plus puissante, 'Lilith MK2' bénéficie du soutien de The World.{N}Qui pourra l'arrêter ?"/>
		<spa name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}¡Lilith se renueva con el nuevo look! Nombre nuevo, 'Lilith MK2'{N}Una 'Lilith MK2' más poderosa con el soporte de The World.{N}¿Quién podrá detenerla?"/>
		<ita name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith si è rifatta il look! Nuovo nome, 'Lilith MK2'{N}Più potente con il supporto di The World.{N}Chi riuscirà a fermarla?"/>
		<rus name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith возвращается в новом виде! Новое имя Lilith MK2! {N}Благодаря поддержке корпорации The World теперь Lilith MK2 стала еще сильнее. {N}Сможете ли вы ее остановить?"/>
		<tur name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith yeni görünümle hayata döndü! Yeni ismi, 'Lilith MK2'{N}The World'ün desteğiyle daha güçlü 'Lilith MK2'.{N}Onu kim durdurabilir ki?"/>
		<twn name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}"/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000071">
		<option red_card="true"/>
		<ger name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith wurde mit neuem Look wiedergeboren! Der neue Name: 'Lilith MK2'.{N}'Lilith MK2' hat jetzt die Unterstützung von The World.{N}Wer kann sie noch aufhalten?"/>
        <eng name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith is revived with new look! New name, 'Lilith MK2'{N}More powerful 'Lilith MK2' with the support of The World.{N}Who can stop her?"/>
		<fre name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith fait son grand retour, plus belle que jamais ! Un nouveau nom 'Lilith MK2'{N}Plus puissante, 'Lilith MK2' bénéficie du soutien de The World.{N}Qui pourra l'arrêter ?"/>
		<spa name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}¡Lilith se renueva con el nuevo look! Nombre nuevo, 'Lilith MK2'{N}Una 'Lilith MK2' más poderosa con el soporte de The World.{N}¿Quién podrá detenerla?"/>
		<ita name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith si è rifatta il look! Nuovo nome, 'Lilith MK2'{N}Più potente con il supporto di The World.{N}Chi riuscirà a fermarla?"/>
		<rus name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith возвращается в новом виде! Новое имя Lilith MK2! {N}Благодаря поддержке корпорации The World теперь Lilith MK2 стала еще сильнее. {N}Сможете ли вы ее остановить?"/>
		<tur name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lilith yeni görünümle hayata döndü! Yeni ismi, 'Lilith MK2'{N}The World'ün desteğiyle daha güçlü 'Lilith MK2'.{N}Onu kim durdurabilir ki?"/>
		<twn name="Frozen Lilith(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}"/>
		<jap name=""/>

		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
        <scenario_list key="5000072">
        <kor name="아마존 워리어" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Der Amazonenkrieger erlegt Raubtiere mit bloßen Händen!{N}Gerüchten zufolge soll er sich von Menschenfleisch ernähren.{N}Seid also vorsichtig, Leaguers!"/>
        <eng name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A valiant Amazon Warrior who caught a beast with his bare hands.{N}Rumor has it that he eats humans so Leaguers need to watch out.{N}Watch out  for Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<fre name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ce Guerrier Amazone a réussi à capturer un monstre de ses mains nues.{N}On raconte qu'il se nourrit de chair humaine : prenez garde !{N}Devenez le Guerrier Amazone !"/>
		<spa name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Amazon Warrior valiente que atrapó a una bestia con sus propias manos.{N}Según los rumores, se alimenta de humanos así que Leaguers, ¡tengan cuidado!{N}¡Busca a Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<ita name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}L'audace guerriero amazzone che catturò una bestia a mani nude.{N}Si dice che mangi gli umani, perciò, state in guardia, giocatori di S4 League!{N}Cercate il guerriero amazzone!"/>
		<rus name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Храбрый амазонский войн поймавший зверя голыми руками.{N}Согласно слухам он ест людей, поэтому участникам лиги стоит его остерегаться.{N}Следите за Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<tur name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bir canavarı çıplak elleriyle yakalayan Valiant Amazon Warrior.{N}İnsan yediğine dair söylentileri düşünecek olursak Leaguers, dikkatli olun.{N}Amazon Warrior için takipte olun!"/>
		<twn name="Amazon Warrior(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}"/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	    <scenario_list key="5000073">
		<kor name="아마존 워리어" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Der Amazonenkrieger erlegt Raubtiere mit bloßen Händen!{N}Gerüchten zufolge soll er sich von Menschenfleisch ernähren.{N}Seid also vorsichtig, Leaguers!"/>
        <eng name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A valiant Amazon Warrior who caught a beast with his bare hands.{N}Rumor has it that he eats humans so Leaguers need to watch out.{N}Watch out  for Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<fre name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ce Guerrier Amazone a réussi à capturer un monstre de ses mains nues.{N}On raconte qu'il se nourrit de chair humaine : prenez garde !{N}Devenez le Guerrier Amazone !"/>
		<spa name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Amazon Warrior valiente que atrapó a una bestia con sus propias manos.{N}Según los rumores, se alimenta de humanos así que Leaguers, ¡tengan cuidado!{N}¡Busca a Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<ita name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}L'audace guerriero amazzone che catturò una bestia a mani nude.{N}Si dice che mangi gli umani, perciò, state in guardia, giocatori di S4 League!{N}Cercate il guerriero amazzone!"/>
		<rus name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Храбрый амазонский войн поймавший зверя голыми руками.{N}Согласно слухам он ест людей, поэтому участникам лиги стоит его остерегаться.{N}Следите за Amazon Warrior!"/>
		<tur name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bir canavarı çıplak elleriyle yakalayan Valiant Amazon Warrior.{N}İnsan yediğine dair söylentileri düşünecek olursak Leaguers, dikkatli olun.{N}Amazon Warrior için takipte olun!"/>
		<twn name="Amazon Warrior(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}"/>
        </scenario_list>
        <scenario_list key="5000074">
        <kor name="아마존 퀸" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lass dich nicht vom Aussehen der Amazonenkönigin täuschen!{N}Gerüchten zufolge soll sie sich von Menschenfleisch ernähren.{N}Seid also vorsichtig, Leaguers!"/>
        <eng name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}She may look like a girl, but she is a valiant Amazon Queen.{N}Rumor has it that she eats humans so Leaguers need to watch out.{N}No one can help you!{N}Watch out for the Amazon Queen!"/>
		<fre name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Parece  una niña ¡pero es una valiente Amazon Queen!!{N}Según los rumores, se alimenta de humanos. Leaguers: ¡tengan cuidado!{N}¡Nadie podrá ayudarte!{N}¡Busca a Amazon Queen!"/>
		<ita name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Sembra una ragazzina eppure è un'audace regina delle Amazzoni!{N}Si dice che mangi gli umani. State in guardia, giocatori di S4 League!{N}Nessuno può aiutarvi!{N}Cercate la regina delle Amazzoni!"/>
		<rus name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Похожа на девушку, но на самом деле она храбрая королева Амазонки!{N}Согласно слухам она ест людей. Участники Лиги: Остерегайтесь ее!{N}Вам никто не сможет помочь! Следите за Amazon Queen!"/>
		<tur name="Amazon Queen(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Kız gibi görünüyor ama aslında bir Valiant Amazon Kraliçesi!{N}İnsan yediğine dair söylentileri düşünecek olursak. Leaguers: dikkatli olun!{N}Kimse size yardım edemez!{N}Amazon Queen için takipte olun!"/>
		<twn name="Frozen Lilith(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}"/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	    <scenario_list key="5000075">
		<kor name="아마존 퀸" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 리그에 찾아온 겨울! 그 겨을 버티기 위한{N}여성 리거의 필수 아이템!! 두꺼운 옷을 입고서도 패션 감각을 놓치지 않는 리거를 위한 아이템!!"/>
		<ger name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Lass dich nicht vom Aussehen der Amazonenkönigin täuschen!{N}Gerüchten zufolge soll sie sich von Menschenfleisch ernähren.{N}Seid also vorsichtig, Leaguers!"/>
        <eng name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}She may look like a girl, but she is a valiant Amazon Queen.{N}Rumor has it that she eats humans so Leaguers need to watch out.{N}No one can help you!{N}Watch out for the Amazon Queen!"/>
		<fre name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Parece  una niña ¡pero es una valiente Amazon Queen!!{N}Según los rumores, se alimenta de humanos. Leaguers: ¡tengan cuidado!{N}¡Nadie podrá ayudarte!{N}¡Busca a Amazon Queen!"/>
		<ita name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Sembra una ragazzina eppure è un'audace regina delle Amazzoni!{N}Si dice che mangi gli umani. State in guardia, giocatori di S4 League!{N}Nessuno può aiutarvi!{N}Cercate la regina delle Amazzoni!"/>
		<rus name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Похожа на девушку, но на самом деле она храбрая королева Амазонки!{N}Согласно слухам она ест людей. Участники Лиги: Остерегайтесь ее!{N}Вам никто не сможет помочь! Следите за Amazon Queen!"/>
		<tur name="Amazon Queen(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Kız gibi görünüyor ama aslında bir Valiant Amazon Kraliçesi!{N}İnsan yediğine dair söylentileri düşünecek olursak. Leaguers: dikkatli olun!{N}Kimse size yardım edemez!{N}Amazon Queen için takipte olun!"/>
