    </scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000084">
        <kor name="로이 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}더월드에서 고용한 넷스피어의 용병 로이!{N}베스 베리와 2인조로 활동하며 돈이 되는 일이라곤 뭐든지 하는 만능 용병.{N}그가 넷스피어에 나타났다. 그 누가 잔악무도한 로이를 막을 수 있을까??"/>
		<ger name="Roy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy, ein Mitglied von 'Netsphere', wurde von 'The World' angeheuert.{N}Am liebsten kämpft er an der Seite seiner Partnerin Beth/Berry, aber auch sonst macht er alles, solange die Bezahlung stimmt.N}Und nun stürzt er sich ins Gefecht, auf der Suche nach einem würdigen Gegner..."/>
        <eng name="Roy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy from Netsphere group who is now currently hired by the group called The World.{N}He loves to team up with his partner Beth/Berry and willing to do anything for money.{N}Now, he joins the show and seeking for someone that can stop him."/>
		<fre name="Roy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy, du groupe Netsphere, travaille maintenant pour le groupe The World.{N} Il adore faire équipe avec Beth/Berry et est prêt à tout pour l'argent.{N} Il se joint maintenant au combat et défie quiconque de l'arrêter."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Roy(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The World grubu tarafından kiralanmış Netsphere grubuna mensup Roy.{N}Partneri Beth/Berry ile takım olup para için her şeyi yapar.{N}Şimdi ise şova katılıyor ve onu durduracak birini arıyor."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000085">
        <kor name="로이 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}더월드에서 고용한 넷스피어의 용병 로이!{N}베스 베리와 2인조로 활동하며 돈이 되는 일이라곤 뭐든지 하는 만능 용병.{N}그가 넷스피어에 나타났다. 그 누가 잔악무도한 로이를 막을 수 있을까??"/>
		<ger name="Roy(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy, ein Mitglied von 'Netsphere', wurde von 'The World' angeheuert.{N}Am liebsten kämpft er an der Seite seiner Partnerin Beth/Berry, aber auch sonst macht er alles, solange die Bezahlung stimmt.N}Und nun stürzt er sich ins Gefecht, auf der Suche nach einem würdigen Gegner..."/>
        <eng name="Roy(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy from Netsphere group who is now currently hired by the group called The World.{N}He loves to team up with his partner Beth/Berry and willing to do anything for money.{N}Now, he joins the show and seeking for someone that can stop him."/>
		<fre name="Roy(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Roy, du groupe Netsphere, travaille maintenant pour le groupe The World.{N} Il adore faire équipe avec Beth/Berry et est prêt à tout pour l'argent.{N} Il se joint maintenant au combat et défie quiconque de l'arrêter."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Roy(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The World grubu tarafından kiralanmış Netsphere grubuna mensup Roy.{N}Partneri Beth/Berry ile takım olup para için her şeyi yapar.{N}Şimdi ise şova katılıyor ve onu durduracak birini arıyor."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000086">
        <kor name="베스 베리 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}평소에는 온순한 모습인 베리! 하지만 그녀에겐 숨겨진 비밀이 있다.{N}누구라도 그녀를 화나게 하면 다른 인격인 베스가 나타나게 된다.{N}베스로 변하게 되면 로이조차도 말리지 못한다고 하는데.. 누가 그녀를 막을 수 있을까?"/>
		<ger name="Beth/Berry(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Zieh keine voreiligen Schlüsse über sie!{N}Und, noch wichtiger: Reiß niemals ihre zweite Persönlichkeit aus ihrem Schlummer –{N}Nichts und niemand sie aufhalten, wenn sie erwacht!"/>
        <eng name="Beth/Berry(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Do not judge someone by her looks.{N} Please do not even try to wake her second personality.{N} Once her second personality is on, there is nobody that can stop her."/>
		<fre name="Beth/Berry(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Les apparences sont parfois trompeuses.{N} N'essayez pas de réveiller la tigresse qui sommeille en elle.{N}Une fois déchaînée, elle est imbattable."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Beth/Berry(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Kimseyi dış görünüşü ile yargılama.{N}Lütfen onun benliğini uyandırmaya çalışma.{N}Eğer bir uyanırsa onu kimse durduramaz."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
		</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000087">
        <kor name="베스 베리 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}평소에는 온순한 모습인 베리! 하지만 그녀에겐 숨겨진 비밀이 있다.{N}누구라도 그녀를 화나게 하면 다른 인격인 베스가 나타나게 된다.{N}베스로 변하게 되면 로이조차도 말리지 못한다고 하는데.. 누가 그녀를 막을 수 있을까?"/>
		<ger name="Beth/Berry(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Zieh keine voreiligen Schlüsse über sie!{N}Und, noch wichtiger: Reiß niemals ihre zweite Persönlichkeit aus ihrem Schlummer –{N}Nichts und niemand sie aufhalten, wenn sie erwacht!"/>
        <eng name="Beth/Berry(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Do not judge someone by her looks.{N}Please do not even try to wake her internal personality.{N}Once her internal personality is on, there is nobody that can stop her."/>
		<fre name="Beth/Berry(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Les apparences sont parfois trompeuses.{N} N'essayez pas de réveiller la tigresse qui sommeille en elle.{N}Une fois déchaînée, elle est imbattable."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Beth/Berry(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Kimseyi dış görünüşü ile yargılama.{N}Lütfen onun benliğini uyandırmaya çalışma.{N}Eğer bir uyanırsa onu kimse durduramaz."/>
