	<scenario_list key="5000088">
        <kor name="샤크 슬레이어 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}무더운 여름이 S4 리그에도 찾아 왔습니다. 모든 리거가 휴양지로 떠나고 있는데요!{N}휴양지에는 무시무시한 상어가 빈번하게 출몰한다고 합니다. 그래도 걱정마세요.{N}샤크 슬레이어가 여러분을 안전하게 지켜줄거예요!!"/>
		<ger name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Wir sind bereit für einen heißen Sommer bei S4 League.{N}Alle Leaguer machen sich auf den Weg in ein Ferienresort.{N}Allerdings wurden zahlreiche blutrünstige Haie an verschiedenen Orten im Resort gesichtet.{N}Aber keine Angst!der Shark Slayer beschützt euch alle!"/>
        <eng name="Shark Slayer(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}We're ready for a hot summer at S4 League.{N}All the leaguers are heading off to a vacation resort.{N}However, vicious sharks have been spotted on numerous occassions at the resort.{N}But don't worry!Shark Slayer will protect all of you!!"/>
		<fre name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}L'été sera très chaud sur S4 League.{N}Tous les leaguers sont partis se dorer la pilule sur une île paradisiaque.{N}Mais de vils requins ont été repérés à plusieurs reprises au large des côtes. Pas de panique !{N}Shark Slayer est là pour vous protéger !!"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 League'de sıcak bir yaza hazırız. Tüm League oyuncuları şu anda tatil köyündeler. {N} Fakat tatil köyünün belirli bölgelerinde vahşi köpek balıkları tespit edildi. Fakat dert etme! {N} Shark Slayer hepinizi koruyacak!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>			
	<scenario_list key="5000089">
         <kor name="샤크 슬레이어 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}무더운 여름이 S4 리그에도 찾아 왔습니다. 모든 리거가 휴양지로 떠나고 있는데요!{N}휴양지에는 무시무시한 상어가 빈번하게 출몰한다고 합니다. 그래도 걱정마세요.{N}샤크 슬레이어가 여러분을 안전하게 지켜줄거예요!!"/>
		<ger name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Wir sind bereit für einen heißen Sommer bei S4 League.{N}Alle Leaguer machen sich auf den Weg in ein Ferienresort.{N}Allerdings wurden zahlreiche blutrünstige Haie an verschiedenen Orten im Resort gesichtet.{N}Aber keine Angst!der Shark Slayer beschützt euch alle!"/>
        <eng name="Shark Slayer(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}We're ready for a hot summer at S4 League.{N}All the leaguers are heading off to a vacation resort.{N}However, vicious sharks have been spotted on numerous occassions at the resort.{N}But don't worry!Shark Slayer will protect all of you!!"/>
		<fre name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}L'été sera très chaud sur S4 League.{N}Tous les leaguers sont partis se dorer la pilule sur une île paradisiaque.{N}Mais de vils requins ont été repérés à plusieurs reprises au large des côtes. Pas de panique !{N}Shark Slayer est là pour vous protéger !!"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Shark Slayer(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}S4 League'de sıcak bir yaza hazırız. Tüm League oyuncuları şu anda tatil köyündeler. {N} Fakat tatil köyünün belirli bölgelerinde vahşi köpek balıkları tespit edildi. Fakat dert etme! {N} Shark Slayer hepinizi koruyacak!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>				
	<scenario_list key="5000090">
        <kor name="샤크 프로텍터 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}포악해 보이기만 하는 상어지만 그녀석들을 지켜주는 리거가 있다고 합니다.{N}그녀의 이름은 샤크 프로텍터!! 샤크 프로텍터의 말에 의하면 상어에게는 숨겨진 온순한 면이 있다고 하는데요!{N}상어를 지키는 그녀의 말을 들어보세요."/>
		<ger name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es gibt eine Leaguerin, die die brutalen Haie beschützt.{N}Ihr Name ist Shark Saviour! Sie ist der Meinung,{N}dass Haie hinter ihren scharfen Zähnen ein sanftes Herz haben.{N}Also, hört auf den Shark Saviour."/>
        <eng name="Shark Protector(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}There's a leaguer that protects the seemingly vicious sharks.{N}Her name is Shark Savior!! According to the Shark Savior,{N}the sharks have a soft heart hidden behind their vicious teeth.{N}Listen to the words of the Shark Savior."/>
		<fre name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un autre leaguer protège cependant ces terribles requins.{N}Il s'agit de Shark Savior !! Selon elle, ces monstres marins se révèlent être très doux malgré leur mâchoire terrifiante."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bu arada görünüşe göre vahşi köpek balıklarını koruyan bir League oyuncusu var.{N}Adı Shark Savior!! Shark Savior'a göre köpek balıkları, vahşi dişlerinin ardında yumuşak bir kalbe sahip.{N}Shark Savior'un sözlerine kulak ver."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>			
	<scenario_list key="5000091">
        <kor name="샤크 프로텍터 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}포악해 보이기만 하는 상어지만 그녀석들을 지켜주는 리거가 있다고 합니다.{N}그녀의 이름은 샤크 프로텍터!! 샤크 프로텍터의 말에 의하면 상어에게는 숨겨진 온순한 면이 있다고 하는데요!{N}상어를 지키는 그녀의 말을 들어보세요."/>
		<ger name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Es gibt eine Leaguerin, die die brutalen Haie beschützt.{N}Ihr Name ist Shark Saviour! Sie ist der Meinung,{N}dass Haie hinter ihren scharfen Zähnen ein sanftes Herz haben.{N}Also, hört auf den Shark Saviour."/>
        <eng name="Shark Protector(Unique)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}There's a leaguer that protects the seemingly vicious sharks.{N}Her name is Shark Savior!! According to the Shark Savior,{N}the sharks have a soft heart hidden behind their vicious teeth.{N}Listen to the words of the Shark Savior."/>
		<fre name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Un autre leaguer protège cependant ces terribles requins.{N}Il s'agit de Shark Savior !! Selon elle, ces monstres marins se révèlent être très doux malgré leur mâchoire terrifiante."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Shark Protector(Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bu arada görünüşe göre vahşi köpek balıklarını koruyan bir League oyuncusu var.{N}Adı Shark Savior!! Shark Savior'a göre köpek balıkları, vahşi dişlerinin ardında yumuşak bir kalbe sahip.{N}Shark Savior'un sözlerine kulak ver."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
<scenario_list key="5000092">
        <kor name="다크 바론 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}해커 G가 만든 새로운 복장! 시즌 8의 또다른 주인공 다크 바론의 복장 !!{N}해커 G가 만들어 낸 진 오필리아의 남자 Ver 복장. 진 오필리아의 폭주를 막기 위한{N}푸른 사슬이 남자 복장에도 적용이 되어 있습니다!!"/>
		<ger name="Dark Baron(Noarmal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ein neues Kostüm, entworfen von Hacker G! Ein Kostüm für Dark Baron, einem neuen Helden der 8. Episode! {N} Kostüm von Hacker G für die männliche Version von Jin Ophelia. Die {N}blaue Kette am Kostüm verhindert Jin Ophelias Überlastung. "/>
        <eng name="Dark Baron(Noarmal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A new costume created by Hacker G! A costume for Dark Baron, another hero of Season 8! {N}Costume for the male version of Jin Ophelia created by the Hacker G.{N}The blue chain that prevents Jin Ophelia from{N}overloading is also equipped on the male costume! "/>
		<fre name="Dark Baron(Noarmal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Nouveau costume conçu par Hacker G ! Costume de Dark Baron, un autre héros de la saison 8 !{N}Costume (H) de Jin Ophelia conçu par Hacker G.{N}La chaîne bleue qui empêche Jin Ophelia de surchauffer est également{N}disponible pour la version masculine du costume ! "/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Dark Baron(Noarmal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Hacker G tarafından yapılmış yeni bir kostüm!{N}Bir diğer Sezon 8 kahramanı Dark Baron için bir kostüm! {N}Hacker G. tarafından Jin Ophelia'nın erkek versiyonu için üretildi.{N}Jin Ophelia'nın aşırı yüklenmesini engelleyen {N}mavi zincir, aynı zamanda erkek kostümünde de bulunuyor! "/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>		
