	<scenario_list key="5000096">
        <kor name="레더호젠 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}축제의 계절이 찾아왔습니다. S4 리그에도 축제의 분위기가 한껏 펼쳐졌는데요.{N}축제의 남주인공 복장 '레더호젠'을 만나보세요.{N}귀여우면서도 젠틀한 복장입니다."/>
		<ger name="Lederhosen (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Festzeit in S4L! Die Festtagsstimmung ist auf dem Höhepunkt! {N}Werft euch in Schale mit dem 'Lederhosen Set' - {N}das perfekte Outfit für jedes Volksfest!"/>
        <eng name="Lederhosen (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The festive season is here. The festive spirit is at its peak in S4L.{N}Have a look at the male hero's 'Lederhosen' costume.{N}It's a cool, casual costume."/>
		<fre name="Lederhosen (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Bayram sezonu başladı! S4L'de bayram havası doruklarda.{N}Erkek kahraman kostümü 'Lederhosen'e bir göz at.{N}Çok havalı ve asil bir kostüm."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Lederhosen (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}La saison festive est arrivée ! La fête bat son plein sur S4L.{N}Jetez un œil au costume pour homme Lederhosen.{N}C'est une tenue sympathique et légère."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>		
