	<scenario_list key="5000106">
        <kor name="에밀리 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}파워즈의 제압을 위해 도미닉에서 급파한 에스퍼 가더 특수 부대원 '에밀리'의 복장!{N}재빠르게 움직일 수 있도록 가볍지만 단단한 소재로 개조되었습니다."/>
		<ger name="Emily (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dieses Kostüm gehört Emily, der S4-Guard-Spezialagentin,{N}die Dominic auf Powers angesetzt hat.{N}Es wurde verbessert, um Emilys Bewegungen noch schneller zu machen,{N}ist aber genauso haltbar wir das Vorgängermodell."/>
        <eng name="Emily (Normal)" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume belonging to Emily, the S4 Guarder Special Agent sent{N}by Dominic to defeat Powers!{N}It's been enhanced to help Emily move faster,{N}yet it retains the structural integrity of its predecessor."/>
