	<scenario_list key="5000108">
        <kor name="스노우 베어 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}스노우 베어 복장만 있다면 추운 겨울도 걱정없어요!!{N}두터운 털로 감싸인 갈색곰으로 완벽 변신!{N}죽은척해도 소용없어요! 어서 도망치세요!"/>
		<ger name="Snow Bear Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dank des Bärenkostüms kann dir der Winter nichts mehr anhaben!{N}Und so warm es ist, so flauschig ist es auch!{N}Wenn du nicht ständig von Fremden gedrückt werden willst,{N}solltest du schnell verschwinden!"/>
        <eng name="Snow Bear Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}There’s no need to worry about the winter{N}as long as you have this snuggly Brown Bear costume!!{N}You are disguised as a fluffy brown bear!{N}It's no use playing dead! Quick, get a move on!"/>
		<fre name="Snow Bear Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Pas de panique. Grâce au costume de Snow Bear, l'hiver ne vous résistera pas !{N}Vous vous êtes transformé en un adorable ours brun tout doux !{N}Il est inutile de simuler votre mort. Fuyez rapidement !"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Snow Bear Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Snow Bear kostümün olduğu sürece kış için endişelenmene gerek yok!!{N}Tam kabarık tüylü bir boz ayıya dönüştün!{N}Ölü taklidi yapsan bile kaçamazsın. Hemen kaç!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000109">
        <kor name="스노우 베어 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}스노우 베어 복장만 있다면 추운 겨울도 걱정없어요!!{N}두터운 털로 감싸인 갈색곰으로 완벽 변신!{N}죽은척해도 소용없어요! 어서 도망치세요!"/>
		<ger name="Snow Bear Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Dank des Bärenkostüms kann dir der Winter nichts mehr anhaben!{N}Und so warm es ist, so flauschig ist es auch!{N}Wenn du nicht ständig von Fremden gedrückt werden willst,{N}solltest du schnell verschwinden!"/>
        <eng name="Snow Bear Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}There’s no need to worry about the winter as long as you have this snuggly{N}Snow Bear costume!!{N}You are disguised as a fluffy brown bear!{N}It's no use playing dead! Quick, get a move on!"/>
		<fre name="Snow Bear Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Pas de panique. Grâce au costume de Snow Bear, l'hiver ne vous résistera pas !{N}Vous vous êtes transformé en un adorable ours brun tout doux !{N}Il est inutile de simuler votre mort. Fuyez rapidement !"/>
