	<scenario_list key="5000110">
        <kor name="스노우 프린세스 일반" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}스노우 베어 복장만 있다면 추운 겨울도 걱정없어요!!{N}두터운 털로 감싸인 갈색곰으로 완벽 변신!{N}죽은척해도 소용없어요! 어서 도망치세요!"/>
		<ger name="Snow Princess Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ein Kostüm aus Schnee und Eis.{N}Die Schneekönigin wird dich darum beneiden!{N}Vielleicht hat sie ihre Schergen bereits auf dich angesetzt ...?"/>
        <eng name="Snow Princess Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}This Snow Princess costume is bejewelled with light dusting of sparkling snow and frost.{N}You'll be more beautiful than the Snow Queen herself!{N}Check out the Snow Princess in all her winter glory!"/>
		<fre name="Snow Princess Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The Snow Princess kostümü kar ve buzdan yapıldı.{N}Karlar kraliçesinden bile daha güzel olabilirsin!{N}Hemen güzeller güzeli Snow Princess'a göz at!"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Snow Princess Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume de Snow Princess fait de neige et de givre.{N}La reine des neiges n'a qu'à bien se tenir !{N}Jetez un coup d'œil au magnifique costume de Snow Princess !"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000111">
        <kor name="스노우 프린세스 유니크" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}스노우 베어 복장만 있다면 추운 겨울도 걱정없어요!!{N}두터운 털로 감싸인 갈색곰으로 완벽 변신!{N}죽은척해도 소용없어요! 어서 도망치세요!"/>
		<ger name="Snow Princess Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ein Kostüm aus Schnee und Eis.{N}Die Schneekönigin wird dich darum beneiden!{N}Vielleicht hat sie ihre Schergen bereits auf dich angesetzt ...?"/>
        <eng name="Snow Princess Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}This Snow Princess costume is bejewelled with light dusting of sparkling snow and frost.{N}You'll be more beautiful than the Snow Queen herself!{N}Check out the Snow Princess in all her winter glory!"/>
		<fre name="Snow Princess Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}The Snow Princess kostümü kar ve buzdan yapıldı.{N}Karlar kraliçesinden bile daha güzel olabilirsin!{N}Hemen güzeller güzeli Snow Princess'a göz at!"/>
