	<scenario_list key="5000122">
        <kor name="Sailor Girl Normal" data=""/>
		<ger name="Sailor Girl Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Ein adretter und doch legerer Matrosinnenlook.{N}Das kleine Kaninchen macht es besonders liebenswert.{N}So kannst auch du in diesem Outfit nur liebenswert und adrett erscheinen!{N}"/>
        <eng name="Sailor Girl Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}A sailor-style schoolgirl's look - playful and stylish.{N}A beautiful rabbit ring completes the look.{N}They'll know you mean business in your Sailor Girl costume!"/>
		<fre name="Sailor Girl Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Style Sailor School.{N}Ensemble décontracté, assorti d'un adorable lapin.{N}Vous serez ravissante dans cette tenue !"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Sailor Girl Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Rahat ve şık Sailor School görünümü.{N}Hem şık hem de sevimli tavşan eklentisi sayesinde son derece güzel.{N}Sailor Girl Costume ile basit ve şık bir imaj!"/>
