			<scenario_list key="5000126">
        <kor name="Valley Rose Normal" data=""/>
		<ger name="Valley Rose Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Wenn du beim nächsten Rockfestival so richtig auffallen willst,{N}ist das Kostüm genau das Richtige!{N}Punkrock kann so sexy sein!{N}Mit diesem Outfit bist du der Hingucker schlechthin!"/>
        <eng name="Valley Rose Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}With this outfit, you're sure to stand out from all{N}the other non-conformists at the upcoming punk festival!{N}You'll be the center of attention with your sexy punk rock style!{N}All you need is the Vallery Rose costume to be the envy of everyone there!"/>
		<fre name="Valley Rose Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Si vous voulez être à la pointe de la mode pour le prochain festival rock,{N}cette tenue est faite pour vous !{N}Tous les regards seront rivés sur vous !{N}Grâce au costume valley rose, la star du jour ce sera vous !"/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Valley Rose Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Yaklaşmakta olan rock festivalinde diğer yenilikçilerden{N}farklı görünmek istiyorsan, işte senin kıyafetin!{N}Seksi punk rock stilinle tüm ilgiyi üstüne çekeceksin!{N}Oradaki herkesi kıskandırmak için ihtiyacın olan tek şey Vallery Rose kostümü!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
