		<scenario_list key="5000132">
        <kor name="UnderBoss Normal" data=""/>
		<ger name="UnderBoss Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255} Dieses trendige Kostüm kombiniert praktische Trainingskleidung mit traditionellem, koreanischen Charme.{N}Die vielen Reißverschlüsse garantieren absolute Bewegungsfreiheit.{N}und sehen auch noch hübsch aus!{N} Dieses Kostüm hat den ersten Platz beim Community Character Design belegt.{N}[Gruppe: Normal (Server.ezs*, Il-DANG-Baek_Gackha)]"/>"/>
        <eng name="UnderBoss Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Season 9 Union First Male Costume.{N}Mafia-style equipment preferred by Neden-based male leaguers.{N}A young boss's classic suit which exudes confidence and style{N}with its matching fur-lined coat and clippers."/>
		<fre name="UnderBoss Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume (M) Union First Season 9.{N}Un fusil d'assaut aux airs maffieux populaire parmi les leaguers de Neden.{N}Ce costume de jeune dirigeant se démarque par son style unique mais élégant.{N}Son col en fourrure et sa coupe ajustée en font un intemporel de la mode."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="UnderBoss Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Sezon 9 Union First Male Costume.{N}Neden'deki ligciler arasında popüler olan mafya tarzı kostüm.{N}Kürk gerdanlık ve makas ile uyumlu,{N}Young Boss'un kendine has ve zarif moda anlayışını gösteren klasik takım elbise tasarımı."/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
