		<scenario_list key="5000134">
        <kor name="Omerta Normal" data=""/>
		<ger name="Omerta Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Season 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Der Mafia-Stil ist sehr beliebt bei den Spielern der Neden-Maps.{N}Basierend auf dem Nadelstreifenanzug, ein Symbol der Mafia, männlich aber sexy.{N}Und passeds zu den Pumps und dem Fedora."/>
        <eng name="Omerta Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Season 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Mafia-style equipment preferred by Neden-based female leaguers.{N}Simultaneously seductive and tough, this pinstriped outfit comes{N}complete with matching fedora and pumps."/>
		<fre name="Omerta Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume (F) Union First Season 9.{N}Un fusil d'assaut aux airs maffieux populaire parmi les leaguers de Neden.{N}Inspiré du célèbre costume rayé typique aux membres de la Mafia, il vous donnera un petit côté garçon manqué mais sexy !{N}Il est fourni avec le chapeau fedora et les chaussures."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Omerta Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Sezon 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Neden'deki ligciler arasında popüler olan mafya tarzı kostüm.{N}Fötr şapka ve ayakkabılar ile uyumlu, mafyanın sembolü olan çizgili desenli.{N}Erkeksi görünümlü ama yine de çok seksi!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
		<scenario_list key="5000135">
        <kor name="Omerta Unique" data=""/>
		<ger name="Omerta Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Season 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Der Mafia-Stil ist sehr beliebt bei den Spielern der Neden-Maps.{N}Basierend auf dem Nadelstreifenanzug, ein Symbol der Mafia, männlich aber sexy.{N}Und passeds zu den Pumps und dem Fedora."/>
        <eng name="Omerta Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Season 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Mafia-style equipment preferred by Neden-based female leaguers.{N}Simultaneously seductive and tough, this pinstriped outfit comes{N}complete with matching fedora and pumps."/>
		<fre name="Omerta Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume (F) Union First Season 9.{N}Un fusil d'assaut aux airs maffieux populaire parmi les leaguers de Neden.{N}Inspiré du célèbre costume rayé typique aux membres de la Mafia, il vous donnera un petit côté garçon manqué mais sexy !{N}Il est fourni avec le chapeau fedora et les chaussures."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<tur name="Omerta Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Sezon 9 Union First Female Costume.{N}Neden'deki ligciler arasında popüler olan mafya tarzı kostüm.{N}Fötr şapka ve ayakkabılar ile uyumlu, mafyanın sembolü olan çizgili desenli.{N}Erkeksi görünümlü ama yine de çok seksi!"/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
		<scenario_list key="5000136">
		<kor name="Net Shaman Luna M Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}넷 스피어의 보안 안드로이드 넷 샤먼 루나의 남성형 아바타 의상.{N}띠와 고리를 활용한 장식으로 주술적인 신비로움을 강조한 독특한 스타일.{N}거친 헤어스타일과 가면, 문신의 조합으로 강렬한 야성미를 어필할 수 있는 의상."/>
		<ger name="Net Shaman Luna M Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Net Sphere Security Android Net Shaman Luna's Costume (Male){N}Dieses eigenwillige Kostüm umfasst zusätzlich eine Schärpe und einen Ring. Das gewisse Etwas!{N}Dieses Kostüm macht dich zu einem toughen Kerl. Es besteht aus einer rebellischen Frisur, einer Maske und einem Tattoo."/>
		<eng name="Net Shaman Luna M Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Net Sphere Security Android Net Shaman Luna's Costume (Male){N}This unique style includes the addition of a sash and ring. It's got that mysterious,{N}magical look to it!{N}This costume has a certain raw appeal. It consists of a rebellious hairstyle, mask, and tattoo."/>
		<fre name="Net Shaman Luna M Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Costume Net Sphere Security Android Net Shaman Luna (H){N}Unique grâce à sa ceinture et à son anneau indémodables. En plus, on dirait qu'il est magique... {N}Quel charme bestial ! Composé d'une coiffure, d'un masque et de tatouages rebelles."/>
		<spa name=""/>
		<ita name=""/>
		<rus name=""/>
		<tur name="Net Shaman Luna M Normal" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}Net Sphere Security Android Net Shaman Luna's Costume (Male){N}Ekstra kuşak ve yüzük de bu tarzın bir parçası. Gizemli, büyülü bir görüntüsü var!{N}Bu kostümde ham bir çekicilik var. Asi bir saç tarzı, maske ve dövmeden oluşuyor."/>
		<tha name=""/>
		<twn name=""/>
		<jap name=""/>
		<idn name=""/>
	</scenario_list>
	<scenario_list key="5000137">
		<kor name="Net Shaman Luna M Unique" data="{N}{A-L}{F-2002_11}{CB-255,255,255,255}넷 스피어의 보안 안드로이드 넷 샤먼 루나의 남성형 아바타 의상.{N}띠와 고리를 활용한 장식으로 주술적인 신비로움을 강조한 독특한 스타일.{N}거친 헤어스타일과 가면, 문신의 조합으로 강렬한 야성미를 어필할 수 있는 의상."/>
